queries.question: List the number of provinces each river flows through.
queries.query_string:
SELECT river, COUNT(province.name) AS number_of_provinces
FROM river
JOIN riverthrough ON river.name = riverthrough.river
JOIN province ON riverthrough.lake = province.name
GROUP BY river

queries.question: Tell me the economy of the Caribbean Sea.
queries.query_string:
SELECT e.country, e.gdp, e.agriculture, e.service, e.industry, e.inflation, e.unemployment 
FROM economy e 
JOIN geo_sea gs ON e.country = gs.country 
WHERE gs.sea = 'Caribbean Sea'
ORDER BY e.gdp DESC;

queries.question: Select cities whose population is greater than 100000, altitude greater than 2500, and the country you belong to has population growth greater than 1.
queries.query_string:
SELECT city.name, city.country, city.population, city.elevation
FROM city
JOIN countrypops ON city.country = countrypops.country
WHERE city.population > 100000 AND city.elevation > 2500 AND countrypops.population > 1
ORDER BY city.population DESC
;

queries.question: For all countries, give the sum of the population of all its neighbors
queries.query_string:
SELECT b.country1, SUM(cp.population) AS total_population
FROM borders b
JOIN countrypops cp ON b.country2 = cp.country
GROUP BY b.country1
ORDER BY total_population DESC;

queries.question: The codes of all countries for which at least one river that originates in this country has its estuary in a neighboring country.
queries.query_string:
SELECT DISTINCT gr.country
FROM geo_river gr
JOIN geo_estuary ge ON gr.river = ge.river
JOIN borders b ON gr.country = b.country1 AND ge.country = b.country2
WHERE gr.country != ge.country

queries.question: The codes of all countries where at least one mountain is located in each of their provinces
queries.query_string:
SELECT DISTINCT c.code
FROM country c
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM province p
    WHERE p.country = c.code
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM geo_mountain gm
        WHERE gm.province = p.name
        AND gm.country = p.country
    )
)

queries.question: The code and total border lengths of all countries with at least one border.
queries.query_string:
SELECT c.code, SUM(b.length) as total_border_length
FROM country c
JOIN borders b ON c.code = b.country1 OR c.code = b.country2
GROUP BY c.code

queries.question: What is the average infant mortality rate for each continent?
queries.query_string:
SELECT continent.name AS Continent, AVG(population.infant_mortality) AS Average_Infant_Mortality
FROM continent
JOIN country ON continent.name = country.province
JOIN population ON country.code = population.country
GROUP BY continent.name;

queries.question: Which country had the lowest population growth?
queries.query_string:
SELECT cp1.country, (cp2.population - cp1.population) as growth
FROM countrypops cp1
JOIN countrypops cp2 ON cp1.country = cp2.country AND cp1.year = cp2.year - 1
ORDER BY growth ASC
FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;

queries.question: What are the area, elevation and type of lakes in country Italy?
queries.query_string:
SELECT l.name, l.area, l.elevation, l.type
FROM lake l
JOIN geo_lake gl ON l.name = gl.lake
JOIN country c ON gl.country = c.code
WHERE c.name = 'Italy'
ORDER BY l.area DESC
LIMIT 5;

queries.question: List the names of capital cities which are the base for organizations in alphabetical order
queries.query_string:
SELECT DISTINCT city.name
FROM city
JOIN organization ON city.name = organization.city AND city.country = organization.country AND city.province = organization.province
WHERE city.name IN (SELECT capital FROM country)
ORDER BY city.name ASC;

queries.question: List the name of organizations that do not have countries with an area smaller than 4000 and of the member type
queries.query_string:
SELECT o.name
FROM organization o
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM ismember m
    JOIN country c ON m.country = c.code
    WHERE m.organization = o.abbreviation AND m.type = 'member' AND c.area < 4000
)

queries.question: List the name of organizations that do not have countries with  an area greater than 10000 and population smaller than 3000 and of the member type
queries.query_string:
SELECT o.name
FROM organization o
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM ismember m
    JOIN country c ON m.country = c.code
    WHERE m.organization = o.abbreviation
    AND m.type = 'member'
    AND c.area > 10000
    AND c.population < 3000
)

queries.question: List the countries that belong to the continent with the largest area

FROM country c

queries.question: List the countries that belong to the continent with the largest area and whose language is English
queries.query_string:
SELECT c.name 
FROM country c 
JOIN encompasses e ON c.code = e.country 
JOIN continent ct ON e.continent = ct.name 
JOIN language l ON c.code = l.country 
WHERE l.name = 'English' AND ct.name = (
    SELECT name 
    FROM continent 
    ORDER BY area DESC 
    FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY
)

queries.question: List all mountains located on islands with an area greater than 100,000 square kilometers
queries.query_string:
SELECT m.name, m.elevation, i.name, i.area
FROM mountain m
JOIN mountainonisland moi ON m.name = moi.mountain
JOIN island i ON moi.island = i.name
WHERE i.area > 100000
ORDER BY i.area DESC
